---
title: Cheesy Pork Schnitzel & Mustard Sauce with Herby Potatoes & Cucumber Cos Salad
description: It’s that time of the week, schnitty night! We’ve been looking forward to showing off this one. A cheesy crumb coats and cooks onto pork to transform it into the ultimate pork schnitzel, especially when drizzled in a creamy mustard sauce.
